21
00:00:43,610 --> 00:00:46,930
changes-- you look at when your inventory position is

22
00:00:46,930 --> 00:00:50,610
less than or equal to the demand times the lead time.

23
00:00:50,610 --> 00:00:53,000
So essentially, you're going to place your order when

24
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:55,700
your inventory position is such that you only

25
