47
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,960
And so items become available incrementally over time,

48
00:01:52,960 --> 00:01:54,010
as I make them.

49
00:01:54,010 --> 00:01:55,780
They don't just come all at once.

50
00:01:55,780 --> 00:01:58,400
And we saw what that leads to is a lower holding

51
00:01:58,400 --> 00:02:01,490
cost because you're making stuff-- as you're making stuff,

52
00:02:01,490 --> 00:02:04,640
